I would like to make a short note to those who are having trouble registering it in Windows 7 64bit. Don't register it when it asks you right after you install it. Close the program, then run as admin. Afterwards, navigate to "activate pro" then c+p the user and serial. Hope this helps someone who made a dumb mistake like me, lol.
